---
<Layout
	title="High-End Washing Machine Repair – Expert Solutions for Your Luxury Laundry Appliance"
	description="Today’s high-end washing machines combine cutting-edge technology with superior build quality, making laundry more efficient and convenient than ever. If your premium washer begins to malfunction, trust <strong>Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci</strong> to deliver the specialized repair it needs. Our brand-certified technicians service top-tier manufacturers like Miele, Bosch, Electrolux, LG, Samsung, and more, ensuring reliable solutions tailored to your specific appliance."
	structuredData={structuredData}
  ogImage="/washer/washing-machne-repair-services.webp"
>
<ParallaxHeader client:idle />
<div style="margin: 50px">

  <h2>HIGH-END & LUXURY WASHING MACHINE REPAIR – PROFESSIONAL & RELIABLE</h2>
  <p>At Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci, we specialize in high-end washing machine repair for brands such as Miele, Gaggenau, ASKO, Bosch, Fisher & Paykel, and Smeg. Our trained technicians combine detailed brand knowledge with white-glove service to restore reliable performance while working carefully around your laundry room, cabinetry, flooring, and surrounding appliances.</p>
<h2>EUROPEAN WASHING MACHINE REPAIR</h2>
<p>European washing machines are often engineered very differently from standard residential washers. Many models feature compact installations, high-speed spin cycles, advanced suspension systems, automatic detergent dosing, water-protection components, specialized drain systems, and model-specific electronics. At Luxury Appliance Repair by Zaricci, we provide European washing machine repair for premium brands such as Gaggenau, Miele, ASKO, Bosch, and Smeg. See below for the most common issues we diagnose and repair.<p/>
</div>
<Tabs1 client:visible/>

<div class="maincontent">
  <h2>What to Expect with Zaricci</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Same-Day Luxury Washing Machine Repair in most areas of Los Angeles, Ventura &amp; Orange County</li>
    <li>Experienced Technicians trained to service luxury &amp; European washing machine models</li>
    <li>Careful Diagnostics for drainage, spin-cycle, leak, vibration, dosing-system &amp; electronic-control issues</li>
    <li>Discreet Service that respects your laundry room, cabinetry, flooring &amp; schedule</li>
    <li>Follow-Up Support to help ensure your washer continues to perform reliably</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Preventative Maintenance for High-End Washing Machines</h3>
  <p>
    Luxury washing machines are an investment. We offer preventative maintenance services designed to preserve performance, reduce the risk of leaks and drainage problems, extend appliance lifespan, and help prevent costly breakdowns — all scheduled around your convenience.
  </p>

  <h2>Washing Machine Repair in Los Angeles, Orange County &amp; Ventura County</h2>
  <p>
    We service high-end washing machines in custom homes, hillside properties, coastal residences, luxury condos, and designer laundry rooms throughout Los Angeles County, Orange County, and Ventura County. Many of these homes include built-in cabinetry, stacked laundry configurations, compact European washers, custom plumbing connections, and premium appliance packages that require careful service and clean workmanship.
  </p>
</div>
<h2>Areas We Serve For Washing Machine Repair</h2>
<p>We service high-end washing machines in custom homes, hillside estates, coastal residences, luxury condos, and designer laundry rooms throughout Los Angeles County, Orange County, and Ventura County. Many of these homes feature front-load washers, compact European washing machines, stacked laundry systems, automatic detergent-dosing models, steam washers, custom cabinetry, specialized plumbing connections, leak-protection systems, and premium appliance packages that require careful diagnostics, precise repair work, and clean, respectful service inside the home.</p>
<Areas client:visible/>
</Layout>

